# 🧠 OS Concept 1: Canary Deployment

🔥 Modern deployment strategy.

---

## 1️⃣ Simple Idea

Instead of releasing update to all users:

👉 release to small percentage first.

---

## Deployment Flow

```text id="n8x2pq"
95% users → old version
5% users → new version
```

Monitor system.

If stable:

✔ expand rollout

If failure:

❌ rollback quickly

---

## 🧠 Real-World Analogy

Restaurant testing new recipe with few customers first.

---

## Why Important?

✔ safer deployments
✔ lower risk
✔ real-user testing

---

## 🔗 Connection

Safer than direct deployment.

Similar goal as blue-green deployment.

---

## 🎯 Placement Question

**Q: Why canary deployment useful?**

👉 Because it reduces deployment risk by exposing updates gradually.

---

## 🧠 Memory Trick

```text id="6v4mtr"
Small rollout first
```

